data.title: Famous birthdays list for November 15, 2023 includes celebrities Winston Duke, Shailene Woodley
data.meta_description: Winston Duke and Shailene Woodley share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of celebrities and other famous people with birthdays on November 15, 2023 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Winston Duke, Shailene Woodley and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on November 15th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on November 15, 2023

Actor Sam Waterston turns 83

Fun fact: His daughter Elisabeth has appeared on ‘Law & Order’ as the daughter of his character

Actress Beverly D’Angelo turns 72

Fun fact: Portrays the same character role originally portrayed by Charlton Heston in the ‘True Lies’ film

Actress Virginie Ledoyen turns 47

Fun fact: Ledoyen is actually one of her grandmothers’ maiden names

Actress Sophia Di Martino turns 40

Fun fact: Appeared on ‘Loki’ as the variant named Sylvie

Actor Winston Duke turns 37

Fun fact: Set to appear in the upcoming film adaptation of ‘The Fall Guy’

Actress Shailene Woodley turns 32

Fun fact: Appeared in several episodes of ‘The District’ early in her acting career

Actress Emma Dumont turns 29

Fun fact: Her middle name is Noelle

More celebrities with birthdays today

Singer Petula Clark is 91. Singer Anni-Frid Lyngstad of ABBA is 78. Actor Bob Gunton (TV’s “24,” film’s “The Shawshank Redemption”) is 78. Actor-director James Widdoes (“Animal House”) is 70. News correspondent John Roberts is 67. Bandleader Kevin Eubanks (“The Tonight Show With Jay Leno”) is 66. Comedian Judy Gold is 61. Actor Rachel True (“Half and Half”) is 57. Rapper E-40 is 56. Country singer Jack Ingram is 53. Actor Jonny Lee Miller (“Elementary,” “Eli Stone”) is 51. Actor Sydney Tamiia Poitier-Heartsong (“Carter,” “Veronica Mars”) is 50. Drummer David Carr of Third Day is 49. Singer Chad Kroeger of Nickelback is 49. Drummer Jesse Sandoval (The Shins) is 49. Actor Sean Murray (“NCIS”) is 46. Rapper B.o.B is 35.
